headline: Caesars underway on $160M renovation, rebrand of Lake Tahoe property
summary: The resort operator is transforming Nevada’s Harveys Lake Tahoe into Caesars Republic Lake Tahoe Hotel & Casino as it prioritizes its regional segment growth.
